; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the auto-xact cost derivation path.  When an automated transaction
; copies a posting that has a total cost (@@), the auto-generated amount
; carries a price annotation with ANNOTATION_PRICE_NOT_PER_UNIT.  When the
; multiplier is negative (-1.0), the generated amount is negative, so
; the cost must be negated

= /Expenses:Electricity/
    (Budget:Electricity)    -1.0

2024/01/01 Electric Bill
    Expenses:Electricity    100 kWh @@ 72 EUR
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Electric Bill         Expenses:Electricity        100 kWh      100 kWh
                                Assets:Cash                  EUR-72       EUR-72
                                                                         100 kWh
                                (Budget:Electricity)       -100 kWh       EUR-72
end test
